titles.title: To reduce temporarily the duty on triethylene glycol bisY3-(3-tert-butyl-4-hydroxy-5-methylphenyl) propionate?.

action.text: Referred to the House Committee on Ways and Means.
Referred to the Subcommittee on Trade.

bill.summary:
12/4/2007--Introduced.
Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to reduce temporarily the duty on triethylene glycol bisY3-(3-tert-butyl-4-hydroxy-5-methylphenyl) propionate?.
